  Research Interests (Keywords) 
Analysis of high-dimensional data, Neuroimaging data, Radiomics, Integrative genomics, and Microbiome.  Statistical decision-making under uncertainty, Multiple comparison problems, Clustering, Bayesian modeling, and Bayesian Nonparametrics.
  Current Positions
Professor, Department of Biostatistics, University of California, Los Angeles.Adjunct Professor, Department of Statistics, Rice University, Houston
